Package: TreeDist
Title: Distances between Phylogenetic Trees
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Martin R.", 'Smith',
                  email="martin.smith@durham.ac.uk", 
                  role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
                  comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5660-1727"))
            )
License: GPL (>= 3)
Description: Implements various measures of tree similarity, including 
  Information-based generalized Robinson-Foulds distances
  (Mutual Phylogenetic Information, Mutual Clustering Information; Smith, in prep); 
  the metric of Nye et al. (2006) <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/bti720>;
  the Matching Split Distance (Bogdanowicz & Giaro 2012) <doi:10.1109/TCBB.2011.48>;
  and the Kendall-Colijn (2016) distance <doi:10.1093/molbev/msw124>.
URL: https://ms609.github.io/TreeDist, https://github.com/ms609/TreeDist
BugReports: https://github.com/ms609/TreeDist/issues
